## Step 6 — post the CLOUD-SHIP RUN record (the completion signal the box reads)
Post a comment on issue #@@ISSUE@@ in @@REPO@@ with EXACTLY this shape (the box parses the header lines and
copies the review text onto the PR it opens):

    CLOUD-SHIP RUN (do not merge by hand — box closes the loop)
